Description: This bag is handcrafted by myself with a beautiful brocade fabric and black pebbled leather. Each computer screen shows colors differently, so what you see on your screen may not accurately show the actual colors Each bag I make is hand cut, and stitched with strong nylon thread on an industrial machine. Back of this gorgeous tote is made of a vintage black leather jacket, silky soft and has a wonderful pebbled texture. This unique bag closes securely with a sturdy magnet feature inside the bag. The shoulder strap is also made from a vintage belt, with a pretty decorative stitch detail. The strap attaches to the purse with antique copper tone swivel clasps and sturdy leather tabs and gun metal rivets. This gorgeous tote measures 11" tall, 14" wide at the bottom, 12" wide at the top. Lastly, I have added a decorative braided leather top closure strap, with really cool buckle, with copper and silver tone studs set in it, on a leather base. Inside is lined in tan canvas, with a double slip pocket. I love combining new, up cycled, and vintage materials, creating a one of a kind bag.
Title: Leather  Boho Gypsy  Tote Purse Bag
